---
import BitCard from '../cards/BitCard.astro';
---

<section id="bits" class="py-24 px-8 md:px-12 bg-surface-container-low border-y-2 border-secondary">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl mb-4">48hrs-bits</h2>
        <p class="font-label text-sm text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Dense fragments of wisdom updated bi-daily.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="hidden md:inline-block font-label text-xs bg-primary text-on-primary px-3 py-1">LIVE FEED</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="columns-1 md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8">
      <BitCard 
        tag="#089 / METAPHYSICS" 
        content="The Ship of Theseus is not a problem of wood, but of identity. Is the 'Self' a collection of parts or a continuity of memory?" 
      />
      <BitCard 
        tag="#090 / ETHICS" 
        content="Utilitarianism fails when it treats the Commissions as a mere variable in a global calculation of pleasure." 
      />
      <BitCard 
        tag="#091 / EXISTENTIALISM" 
        content="Existence precedes essence. You are the architect of your own meaning in a silent universe." 
      />
      <BitCard 
        tag="#092 / PHENOMENOLOGY" 
        content="Brackets are for math and Husserl. Suspend your assumptions about the external world to see the pure phenomenon." 
      />
      <BitCard 
        tag="#093 / LOGIC" 
        content="A straw man argument is a coward's shortcut. Steel-man your opponent if you truly seek truth." 
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex md:hidden justify-center">
      <span class="font-label text-xs bg-primary text-on-primary px-4 py-2">LIVE FEED</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
